\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14835199 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 Alice Foley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012655 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 And your present address?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14835199 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 2, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Burnside Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bolton{\*\xmlclose}, yes.
