Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 . And I suppose it was really what she - she'd had to go through you see. But she never grumbled, she never talked about it. Only just occasionally she would
 just say, well, you live your own life but don't get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13978893 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 
. I don't say that that's influenced me at all but it could have - it could have done - could have done. What she went through. Yes.
