very frugal - very frugal - because of although food was cheap in those days what happened was that father and mother - that was perhaps one of the things he might have helped with I don't know - but they used to go down town Saturday nights and they used
 
to - wait - well off - just occasionally when I was growing older I went with them because I can remember Newport Street being ablaze with the gas jets and all the shops used to keep open 'til about eleven and twelve o'clock in those days. And the butcher
s
