 - she was the one although I can never say we were pals, you see, I can't say we were pals. But - it was strange that I was an }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5603085\charrsid11536143 acutely}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
