y because I believe that the grandmother on his side - his mother - was - well my mother always said what a - what a lovely women she was you see, I don't know but - the - I - I remember as quite a tiny child - going with her to the pawn shop and I used t
o
 like very much going to the pawn shop and I used to watch her parceling all these things up on a Monday morning, and then we'd trop off to the little - the pawn shop. And I liked going because the man who - was in charge of the pawn shop was one of the D
