ightened at my - my time was Tootle Broadhurst Lees. And they were enlightened because they - they started a - a cont - a day }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568115\charrsid11536143 continuation}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143  school, you see, that all girls and boys going into the mill at fourteen had to have certain half days off and attend their school - there - there, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012655 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 And about when would that be?
