\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11012655 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 Were there sufficient then abouts to have pensions and profit sharing schemes?
