 of opportunity, you see, and it never - no, I wouldn't say it changed it at all in fact - in fact I should think it rather strengthened it you see, than weakened it at all and - my only probably, feeling is that we worked so hard to do so much for the pe
ople that we represented and that now so many of those ideals have gone by the board, you see, you - you look back and you think to yourself, oh dear - you see, I fought so hard for Saturday morning because I wanted the women to have Saturday morning. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 I fou
