 a half Saturday morning and they would fight to go }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568115\charrsid11536143 on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 
on a Saturday morning and the women at first refused, you see, and there were all this struggle and now quite a lot of the women have given way on it. Not all of them - a lot don't go in - it has to be 
