 church went out later on and there was just the Labour party and this Socialist Sunday school but most of the people who were - who had supported the Labour party joined the Socialist Sunday School, see what I mean - the Labour church I mean, because the
 
room was taken off them. Their rooms that they were having were taken off them or it was that the rent increased enormously and they couldn't afford to continue or it might have been that they were unable to get the speakers and pay the expenses because t
