ps where there was a wide variety of different speakers representing various religions and political opinion who were received with good natured heckling but without any kind of rowdyism at that time. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 These meetings were held on Sundays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14835199 AF  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 Would have s
o long, perhaps half an hour, and then he would step down and somebody else would - hold forth - it might have been an atheist used to have a lot of atheists come along and they would hold forth. Again the crowd would - some would leave, some would - }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265682\charrsid11536143 others}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 
 would join it and again there would be good natured heckling and people quoting Bible - things - things in the Bible that they didn't think was true and all that kind of thing. Then there would probably be a - a - one or two politicians. There would be, 
