n to be treated in this }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265682\charrsid11536143 patronizing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6489771\charrsid11536143 
 way - we'll fill the church ab - absolutely to the church doors with our mill people you see and I - I could see through it - the other - quite a lot of the girls thought it was wonderful, you see, to be invited, you see,
