 about the work people going in the toilets and smoking cigarettes and this always hit me, you see, and I used to think to myself why do they keep }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4265682\charrsid11536143 grumbling}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
